{"title":"欢呼党中央的决定","authors":["张小冲　张品"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼党中央的决定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京四中高一（一）班　张小冲　张品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命的洪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩荡荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一声春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震动四面八方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底改革教育制度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一切旧意识埋葬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这英明的决定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打碎了科举式的考场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸烂了产生精神贵族的温床。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹遍了校园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处一片新生景象。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这决定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大长了革命青年的志气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们斗志昂扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战无不胜的毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们胜利的源泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们前进的方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您，给了我们强大的思想武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您，教导我们做革命的闯将。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼呀，跳跃呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心在歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与工农兵相结合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在斗争中成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横扫一切牛鬼蛇神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向光辉的前方！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}